quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  7,109,Kheun treuk awak nyan sihe atra nyoe Carong that jih nyoe ‘eleumee luah
  7,110,Jimeung peuteubiet gata lam nanggroe Teuh pakri jinoe teuma tapeugah
  7,111,Jikheun treuk teuma tayue preh bak jih Deungon aduen jih jipiyoh payah Tajak krah rakyat dum dalam nanggroe Tayue jak keunoe bandum beubagah
  7,112,Tayue jak bandum ngon tukang sihe Nyang carong pike bak mita ilah
  7,113,Tukang sihe troh dum bak Peuraʻeun Watee nyan jikheun na tabri upah Upah keu kamoe meu kamoe meunang
  7,114,Seuot Peuraʻeun bandum na upah Gata dum teuma lom toe ngon raja Ureueng mulia hana ban peugah
  7,115,Kheun treuk awak nyan hai Musa pakri i Soe nyang mulai peuleumah tuah Kamoe tiek dilee atawa gata
  7,116,Gata phon mula Musa kheun bagah ‘Oh ban dum jitiek ‘eleumee sihe Teumakot ate ureueng yo leupah Jimevʻen sulap jibalek mata Sihe that raya ‘ajeb sileupah
  7,117,Kamoe beri wahyu teuma bak Musa Tiek tungkat gata jinoe tabalah ‘Oh ban ka geutiek tungkat le Musa Jiʻuet le sigra peue nyang meurimbah Abeh dum jiʻuet sihe awak nyan
  7,118,Nyata le yoh nyan beuna ngon salah Kakeuh beh bateue peue nyang jipeugot Musa beuna that ka trang sileupah
  7,119,Ka abeh talo bandum jih sinan Jiwoe le yoh nyan malee that leupah
  7,120,Tukang sihe dum teuma jisujud
  7,121,Jikheun cit patot kamoe nyang kalah Kamoe meuiman jinoe keu Tuhan Nyang Po dum alam deungon blah bicah
  7,122,Keu Tuhan Musa ngon Tuhan Harun
  7,123,Kheun treuk Peuraʻeun beungeh jih leupah Peue tameuiman keu jih dum gata Bak lon nyang raja hana tapeugah Goh lom kuidin dilon keu gata Bit tipee daya tapeugot ulah Tapeugot kaco di dalam kuta Tayue keulua rakyat tan salah Tameung peuteubiet rakyat u lua Tateupeue sigra akan kubalah
  7,124,Kukoh jaroeteuh beu sirong sareng Gaki wie uneuen kukoh siblah-blah Lheueh nyan kusula bandum kuteupang
  7,125,Seuot awak nyan kamoe ikheulah Kamoe keumeung woe bak Tuhan kamoe
  7,126,Digata jinoe tameung tueng balah Gata tueng balah teuma bak kamoe Sabab dum kamoe iman keu Allah Kamoe meupateh ayat Po kamoe Ka troh bak kamoe Musa jak peugah Beu ek meusaba wahe Po kamoe Beu mate kamoe dalam meunyeurah Beu mate kamoe dalam Iseulam